ave with the same amount of experience I had before entering. I do NOT have fun when I spend an hour running from one place to another because I cant find a soloing druid or wizard who has the time to sell me a port to wherever. I do NOT have fun when a mob that is 10 levels under me totally kicks my ass.<br><br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
