d to be tedious work.  At least in EQ, the extreme downtime gives me plenty of time to do things like clean the house, etc while I am waiting for groups, waiting for rez, waiting for mana, etc.  <br><br>Well that was some pretty severe rambling on my part hope it is somewhat readable.<br><br>-- Natascha<br>-- Abigaile Myrrh<br><br><br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Abigaile Myrrh of Clan Blackwatch<br>Cazic Server</td></tr>
